{"tid":1235421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個背影 我地每個人都好熟識","createTime":"2019-06-17T06:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:40:40.000Z","uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20d2ec21e637c224b75d429c2734a76ecc2feb67","tid":1235421,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFgTpR7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFgTpR7.jpg&h=6a104ae9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兵不厭詐 一場抗爭之後人係會攰 當場既憤怒同士氣亦都會淡化<br />\n但唔好唔記得即使呢個林奠係到玩拖延戰 <br />\n我地已經有烈士死左 學生義士受場比人捉左<br />\n有老豆癌症出黎又比黑警老屈 又有人比人翻舊帳6月12請假被炒<br />\n唔排除亦都有更多人比人捉<br />\n我地香港人損失左太多 如果呢一刻放棄<br />\n或者比三毛搞到內哄分化 就會辜負曬呢班捨身達義既勇士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地香港人 唔怕死 不畏懼 繼續奮戰！！！ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地戰爭口號：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不犧牲 不分化 不篤灰 不撤退 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申發夢</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c73130c5b15bc61a5501e9ac49b19a25936a3da","tid":1235421,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623c86c794b54110b7b6904caad8389824575b29","tid":1235421,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d8b9c478e46b864e5f1bf8bafe4c3e232ab0a5","tid":1235421,"uid":41389,"